<h1 class="headline">100-year-old marathoner sets record in Toronto</h1>
<h3 class="deck">Fauja Singh finishes in 8 hours to become oldest person to complete full marathon</h3>
<h5 class="byline">

The Associated Press
</h5>

<h4 class="posted">Posted:

Oct 16, 2011   7:44 PM ET


</h4>

<h4 class="lastupdated">Last Updated: 

Oct 16, 2011   7:41 PM ET


